;;;;FILE:               substitute
;;;;LANGUAGE:           Common-Lisp
;;;;SYSTEM:             Common-Lisp
;;;;USER-INTERFACE:     NONE
;;;;DESCRIPTION
;;;;
;;;;    A strange substitution:
;;;;
;;;;    'ab*c' 'xyz'
;;;;    dacdddddd     -->   dxydddddd
;;;;    dabcddddd     -->   dxyzddddd
;;;;    dabbbcddd     -->   dxyzxyddd
;;;;    dabbbbbcd     -->   dxyzxyzxd
;;;;
